Morton Int ' l spin - off will be tax - free . Morton International Inc said Monday the Internal Revenue Service has determined that the upcoming spin - off of its specialty chemicals and salt businesses will be tax - free to its shareholders . Morton is also combining its Automotive Safety Products business with Autoliv AB , the Swedish car safety equipment maker . Morton shareholders are scheduled to vote on the proposal at a special meeting scheduled for April 24 . Morton and Autoliv expect the transactions to close by early May . Morton shares closed up 1 / 4 Monday at 43 . ( ( Chicago newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
